SUMMARY:Setting Up Your Personal AI Squad — Demo by Tamir
LOCATION:Microsoft Teams Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Hey team! I want to show you how I set up a personal AI squad
  that works autonomously — researches\, codes\, monitors\, and reports
  back to me.\n\nWhat I'll cover:\n- Squad setup — how to hire your AI
  team with roles\, charters\, and memory\n- Ralph — the autonomous loop
  that works while you sleep\n- Live Monitor — see what your agents are
  doing in real-time\n- Teams/Email scanning — agents that silently
  monitor your channels\n- Podcaster — auto-generate audio summaries\n-
  News Reporter — styled briefings delivered to Teams\n- Tools we built
  — scheduler\, dashboard\, cross-squad orchestration\n\nThis is NOT a
  product pitch — it's me sharing what I built for myself. Bring your
  laptop if you want to try it live.
